var book = {
	"name": "Galatians",
	"numChapters": 6,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29059A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29059A\"></sup>an apostle (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29059B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29059B\"></sup>not <i>sent</i> from men nor through the agency of man, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29059C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29059C\"></sup>through Jesus Christ and God the Father, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29059D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29059D\"></sup>raised Him from the dead),",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29060E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29060E\"></sup>the brethren who are with me,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29060F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29060F\"></sup>the churches of Galatia:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29061G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29061G\"></sup>Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29062H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29062H\"></sup>gave Himself for our sins so that He might rescue us from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29062I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29062I\"></sup>this present evil age, according to the will of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29062J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29062J\"></sup>our God and Father,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29063K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29063K\"></sup>to whom <i>be</i> the glory forevermore. Amen.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I am amazed that you are so quickly deserting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29064L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29064L\"></sup>Him who called you by the grace of Christ, for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29064M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29064M\"></sup>different gospel;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>which is <i>really</i> not another; only there are some who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29065N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29065N\"></sup>disturbing you and want to distort the gospel of Christ.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But even if we, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29066O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29066O\"></sup>an angel from heaven, should preach to you a gospel contrary to what we have preached to you, he is to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29066P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29066P\"></sup>accursed!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29067Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29067Q\"></sup>have said before, so I say again now, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29067R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29067R\"></sup>if any man is preaching to you a gospel contrary to what you received, he is to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29067S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29067S\"></sup>accursed!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For am I now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29068T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29068T\"></sup>seeking the favor of men, or of God? Or am I striving to please men? If I were still trying to please men, I would not be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29068U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29068U\"></sup>bond-servant of Christ.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29069V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29069V\"></sup>I would have you know, brethren, that the gospel which was preached by me is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29069W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29069W\"></sup>not according to man.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29070X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29070X\"></sup>I neither received it from man, nor was I taught it, but <i>I received it</i> through a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29070Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29070Y\"></sup>revelation of Jesus Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For you have heard of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29071Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29071Z\"></sup>my former manner of life in Judaism, how I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29071AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29071AA\"></sup>used to persecute <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29071AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29071AB\"></sup>the church of God beyond measure and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29071AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29071AC\"></sup>tried to destroy it;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29072AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29072AD\"></sup>was advancing in Judaism beyond many of my contemporaries among my countrymen, being more extremely zealous for my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29072AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29072AE\"></sup>ancestral traditions.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But when God, who had set me apart <i>even</i> from my mother’s womb and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29073AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29073AF\"></sup>called me through His grace, was pleased",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>to reveal His Son in me so that I might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29074AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29074AG\"></sup>preach Him among the Gentiles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29074AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29074AH\"></sup>I did not immediately consult with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29074AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29074AI\"></sup>flesh and blood,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29075AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29075AJ\"></sup>nor did I go up to Jerusalem to those who were apostles before me; but I went away to Arabia, and returned once more to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29075AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29075AK\"></sup>Damascus.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29076AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29076AL\"></sup>three years later I went up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29076AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29076AM\"></sup>to Jerusalem to become acquainted with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29076AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29076AN\"></sup>Cephas, and stayed with him fifteen days.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But I did not see any other of the apostles except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29077AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29077AO\"></sup>James, the Lord’s brother.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>(Now in what I am writing to you, I assure you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29078AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29078AP\"></sup>before God that I am not lying.)",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29079AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29079AQ\"></sup>I went into the regions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29079AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29079AR\"></sup>Syria and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29079AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29079AS\"></sup>Cilicia.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I was <i>still</i> unknown by sight to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29080AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29080AT\"></sup>the churches of Judea which were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29080AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29080AU\"></sup>in Christ;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>but only, they kept hearing, “He who once persecuted us is now preaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29081AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29081AV\"></sup>the faith which he once <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29081AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29081AW\"></sup>tried to destroy.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29082AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29082AX\"></sup>were glorifying God because of me."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Then after an interval of fourteen years I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29083A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29083A\"></sup>went up again to Jerusalem with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29083B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29083B\"></sup>Barnabas, taking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29083C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29083C\"></sup>Titus along also.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>It was because of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29084D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29084D\"></sup>revelation that I went up; and I submitted to them the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29084E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29084E\"></sup>gospel which I preach among the Gentiles, but <i>I did so</i> in private to those who were of reputation, for fear that I might be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29084F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29084F\"></sup>running, or had run, in vain.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But not even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29085G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29085G\"></sup>Titus, who was with me, though he was a Greek, was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29085H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29085H\"></sup>compelled to be circumcised.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But <i>it was</i> because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29086I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29086I\"></sup>false brethren secretly brought in, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29086J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29086J\"></sup>had sneaked in to spy out our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29086K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29086K\"></sup>liberty which we have in Christ Jesus, in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29086L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29086L\"></sup>bring us into bondage.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But we did not yield in subjection to them for even an hour, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29087M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29087M\"></sup>the truth of the gospel would remain with you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But from those who were of high <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29088N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29088N\"></sup>reputation (what they were makes no difference to me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29088O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29088O\"></sup>God shows no partiality)—well, those who were of reputation contributed nothing to me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But on the contrary, seeing that I had been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29089P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29089P\"></sup>entrusted with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29089Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29089Q\"></sup>gospel to the uncircumcised, just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29089R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29089R\"></sup>Peter <i>had been</i> to the circumcised",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>(for He who effectually worked for Peter in <i>his</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29090S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29090S\"></sup>apostleship to the circumcised effectually worked for me also to the Gentiles),",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and recognizing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29091T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29091T\"></sup>the grace that had been given to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29091U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29091U\"></sup>James and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29091V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29091V\"></sup>Cephas and John, who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29091W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29091W\"></sup>reputed to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29091X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29091X\"></sup>pillars, gave to me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29091Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29091Y\"></sup>Barnabas the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29091Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29091Z\"></sup>right hand of fellowship, so that we <i>might</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29091AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29091AA\"></sup><i>go</i> to the Gentiles and they to the circumcised.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><i>They</i> only <i>asked</i> us to remember the poor—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29092AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29092AB\"></sup>the very thing I also was eager to do.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29093AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29093AC\"></sup>Cephas came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29093AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29093AD\"></sup>Antioch, I opposed him to his face, because he stood condemned.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For prior to the coming of certain men from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29094AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29094AE\"></sup>James, he used to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29094AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29094AF\"></sup>eat with the Gentiles; but when they came, he <i>began</i> to withdraw and hold himself aloof, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29094AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29094AG\"></sup>fearing the party of the circumcision.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The rest of the Jews joined him in hypocrisy, with the result that even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29095AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29095AH\"></sup>Barnabas was carried away by their hypocrisy.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when I saw that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29096AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29096AI\"></sup>were not straightforward about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29096AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29096AJ\"></sup>the truth of the gospel, I said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29096AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29096AK\"></sup>Cephas in the presence of all, “If you, being a Jew, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29096AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29096AL\"></sup>live like the Gentiles and not like the Jews, how <i>is it that</i> you compel the Gentiles to live like Jews? ",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“We <i>are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29097AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29097AM\"></sup>Jews by nature and not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29097AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29097AN\"></sup>sinners from among the Gentiles;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>nevertheless knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29098AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29098AO\"></sup>a man is not justified by the works of the Law but through faith in Christ Jesus, even we have believed in Christ Jesus, so that we may be justified by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29098AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29098AP\"></sup>faith in Christ and not by the works of the Law; since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29098AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29098AQ\"></sup>by the works of the Law no flesh will be justified.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But if, while seeking to be justified in Christ, we ourselves have also been found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29099AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29099AR\"></sup>sinners, is Christ then a minister of sin? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29099AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29099AS\"></sup>May it never be!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For if I rebuild what I have <i>once</i> destroyed, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29100AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29100AT\"></sup>prove myself to be a transgressor.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For through the Law I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29101AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29101AU\"></sup>died to the Law, so that I might live to God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29102AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29102AV\"></sup>crucified with Christ; and it is no longer I who live, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29102AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29102AW\"></sup>Christ lives in me; and the <i>life</i> which I now live in the flesh I live by faith in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29102AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29102AX\"></sup>the Son of God, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29102AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29102AY\"></sup>loved me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29102AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29102AZ\"></sup>gave Himself up for me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I do not nullify the grace of God, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29103BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29103BA\"></sup>if righteousness <i>comes</i> through the Law, then Christ died needlessly.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>You foolish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29104A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29104A\"></sup>Galatians, who has bewitched you, before whose eyes Jesus Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29104B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29104B\"></sup>was publicly portrayed <i>as</i> crucified?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is the only thing I want to find out from you: did you receive the Spirit by the works of the Law, or by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29105C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29105C\"></sup>hearing with faith?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Are you so foolish? Having begun by the Spirit, are you now being perfected by the flesh?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Did you suffer so many things in vain—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29107D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29107D\"></sup>if indeed it was in vain?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So then, does He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29108E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29108E\"></sup>provides you with the Spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29108F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29108F\"></sup>works miracles among you, do it by the works of the Law, or by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29108G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29108G\"></sup>hearing with faith?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Even so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29109H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29109H\"></sup>Abraham <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29109I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29109I\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">believed God, and it was reckoned to him as righteousness</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore, be sure that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29110J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29110J\"></sup>it is those who are of faith who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29110K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29110K\"></sup>sons of Abraham.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Scripture, foreseeing that God would justify the Gentiles by faith, preached the gospel beforehand to Abraham, <i>saying</i>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29111L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29111L\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">All the nations will be blessed in you</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">.</span>”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29112M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29112M\"></sup>those who are of faith are blessed with Abraham, the believer.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For as many as are of the works of the Law are under a curse; for it is written, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29113N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29113N\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Cursed is everyone who does not abide by all things written in the book of the law, to perform them</span>.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29114O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29114O\"></sup>no one is justified by the Law before God is evident; for, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29114P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29114P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The righteous man shall live by faith</span>.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>However, the Law is not of faith; on the contrary, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29115Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29115Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He who practices them shall live</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">by them</span>.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29116R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29116R\"></sup>redeemed us from the curse of the Law, having become a curse for us—for it is written, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29116S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29116S\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Cursed is everyone who hangs on</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29116T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29116T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">a</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">tree</span>”—",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>in order that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29117U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29117U\"></sup>in Christ Jesus the blessing of Abraham might come to the Gentiles, so that we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29117V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29117V\"></sup>would receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29117W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29117W\"></sup>the promise of the Spirit through faith.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29118X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29118X\"></sup>Brethren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29118Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29118Y\"></sup>I speak in terms of human relations: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29118Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29118Z\"></sup>even though it is <i>only</i> a man’s covenant, yet when it has been ratified, no one sets it aside or adds conditions to it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now the promises were spoken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29119AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29119AA\"></sup>to Abraham and to his seed. He does not say, “And to seeds,” as <i>referring</i> to many, but <i>rather</i> to one, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29119AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29119AB\"></sup>And to your seed,” that is, Christ.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>What I am saying is this: the Law, which came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29120AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29120AC\"></sup>four hundred and thirty years later, does not invalidate a covenant previously ratified by God, so as to nullify the promise.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29121AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29121AD\"></sup>if the inheritance is based on law, it is no longer based on a promise; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29121AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29121AE\"></sup>God has granted it to Abraham by means of a promise.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29122AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29122AF\"></sup>Why the Law then? It was added because of transgressions, having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29122AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29122AG\"></sup>ordained through angels <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29122AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29122AH\"></sup>by the agency of a mediator, until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29122AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29122AI\"></sup>the seed would come to whom the promise had been made.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29123AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29123AJ\"></sup>a mediator is not for one <i>party only</i>; whereas God is <i>only</i> one.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Is the Law then contrary to the promises of God? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29124AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29124AK\"></sup>May it never be! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29124AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29124AL\"></sup>if a law had been given which was able to impart life, then righteousness would indeed have been based on law.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But the Scripture has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29125AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29125AM\"></sup>shut up everyone under sin, so that the promise by faith in Jesus Christ might be given to those who believe.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But before faith came, we were kept in custody under the law, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29126AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29126AN\"></sup>being shut up to the faith which was later to be revealed.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore the Law has become our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29127AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29127AO\"></sup>tutor <i>to lead us</i> to Christ, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29127AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29127AP\"></sup>we may be justified by faith.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But now that faith has come, we are no longer under a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29128AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29128AQ\"></sup>tutor.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For you are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29129AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29129AR\"></sup>sons of God through faith in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29129AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29129AS\"></sup>Christ Jesus.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For all of you who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29130AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29130AT\"></sup>baptized into Christ have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29130AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29130AU\"></sup>clothed yourselves with Christ.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29131AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29131AV\"></sup>There is neither Jew nor Greek, there is neither slave nor free man, there is neither male nor female; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29131AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29131AW\"></sup>you are all one in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29131AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29131AX\"></sup>Christ Jesus.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29132AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29132AY\"></sup>you belong to Christ, then you are Abraham’s descendants, heirs according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29132AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29132AZ\"></sup>promise."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Now I say, as long as the heir is a child, he does not differ at all from a slave although he is owner of everything,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>but he is under guardians and managers until the date set by the father.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So also we, while we were children, were held <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29135A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29135A\"></sup>in bondage under the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29135B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29135B\"></sup>elemental things of the world.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29136C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29136C\"></sup>the fullness of the time came, God sent forth His Son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29136D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29136D\"></sup>born of a woman, born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29136E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29136E\"></sup>under the Law,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>so that He might redeem those who were under the Law, that we might receive the adoption as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29137F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29137F\"></sup>sons.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Because you are sons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29138G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29138G\"></sup>God has sent forth the Spirit of His Son into our hearts, crying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29138H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29138H\"></sup>Abba! Father!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore you are no longer a slave, but a son; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29139I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29139I\"></sup>if a son, then an heir through God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>However at that time, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29140J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29140J\"></sup>when you did not know God, you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29140K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29140K\"></sup>slaves to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29140L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29140L\"></sup>those which by nature are no gods.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But now that you have come to know God, or rather to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29141M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29141M\"></sup>known by God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29141N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29141N\"></sup>how is it that you turn back again to the weak and worthless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29141O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29141O\"></sup>elemental things, to which you desire to be enslaved all over again?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29142P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29142P\"></sup>observe days and months and seasons and years.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I fear for you, that perhaps I have labored over you in vain.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I beg of you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29144Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29144Q\"></sup>brethren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29144R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29144R\"></sup>become as I <i>am</i>, for I also <i>have become</i> as you <i>are</i>. You have done me no wrong;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>but you know that it was because of a bodily illness that I preached the gospel to you the first time;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and that which was a trial to you in my bodily condition you did not despise or loathe, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29146S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29146S\"></sup>you received me as an angel of God, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29146T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29146T\"></sup>Christ Jesus <i>Himself</i>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Where then is that sense of blessing you had? For I bear you witness that, if possible, you would have plucked out your eyes and given them to me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So have I become your enemy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29148U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29148U\"></sup>by telling you the truth?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They eagerly seek you, not commendably, but they wish to shut you out so that you will seek them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But it is good always to be eagerly sought in a commendable manner, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29150V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29150V\"></sup>not only when I am present with you.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29151W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29151W\"></sup>My children, with whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29151X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29151X\"></sup>I am again in labor until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29151Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29151Y\"></sup>Christ is formed in you—",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>but I could wish to be present with you now and to change my tone, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29152Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29152Z\"></sup>I am perplexed about you.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Tell me, you who want to be under law, do you not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29153AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29153AA\"></sup>listen to the law?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For it is written that Abraham had two sons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29154AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29154AB\"></sup>one by the bondwoman and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29154AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29154AC\"></sup>one by the free woman.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29155AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29155AD\"></sup>the son by the bondwoman was born according to the flesh, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29155AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29155AE\"></sup>the son by the free woman through the promise.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29156AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29156AF\"></sup>This is allegorically speaking, for these <i>women</i> are two covenants: one <i>proceeding</i> from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29156AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29156AG\"></sup>Mount Sinai bearing children who are to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29156AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29156AH\"></sup>slaves; she is Hagar.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now this Hagar is Mount Sinai in Arabia and corresponds to the present Jerusalem, for she is in slavery with her children.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29158AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29158AI\"></sup>the Jerusalem above is free; she is our mother.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For it is written,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29159AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29159AJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Rejoice, barren woman who does not bear</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Break forth and shout, you who are not in labor</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For more numerous are the children of the desolate</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Than of the one who has a husband</span>.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And you brethren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29160AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29160AK\"></sup>like Isaac, are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29160AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29160AL\"></sup>children of promise.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But as at that time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29161AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29161AM\"></sup>he who was born according to the flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29161AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29161AN\"></sup>persecuted him <i>who was born</i> according to the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29161AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29161AO\"></sup>so it is now also.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But what does the Scripture say?“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29162AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29162AP\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Cast out the bondwoman and her son</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29162AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29162AQ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the son of the bondwoman shall not be an heir with the son of the free woman</span>.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So then, brethren, we are not children of a bondwoman, but of the free woman."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29164A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29164A\"></sup>It was for freedom that Christ set us free; therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29164B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29164B\"></sup>keep standing firm and do not be subject again to a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29164C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29164C\"></sup>yoke of slavery.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Behold I, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29165D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29165D\"></sup>Paul, say to you that if you receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29165E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29165E\"></sup>circumcision, Christ will be of no benefit to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29166F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29166F\"></sup>testify again to every man who receives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29166G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29166G\"></sup>circumcision, that he is under obligation to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29166H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29166H\"></sup>keep the whole Law.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You have been severed from Christ, you who are seeking to be justified by law; you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29167I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29167I\"></sup>fallen from grace.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For we through the Spirit, by faith, are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29168J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29168J\"></sup>waiting for the hope of righteousness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29169K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29169K\"></sup>Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29169L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29169L\"></sup>neither circumcision nor uncircumcision means anything, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29169M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29169M\"></sup>faith working through love.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29170N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29170N\"></sup>running well; who hindered you from obeying the truth?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>This persuasion <i>did</i> not <i>come</i> from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29171O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29171O\"></sup>Him who calls you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29172P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29172P\"></sup>A little leaven leavens the whole lump <i>of dough</i>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29173Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29173Q\"></sup>I have confidence in you in the Lord that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29173R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29173R\"></sup>will adopt no other view; but the one who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29173S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29173S\"></sup>disturbing you will bear his judgment, whoever he is.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But I, brethren, if I still preach circumcision, why am I still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29174T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29174T\"></sup>persecuted? Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29174U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29174U\"></sup>the stumbling block of the cross has been abolished.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I wish that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29175V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29175V\"></sup>those who are troubling you would even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29175W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29175W\"></sup>mutilate themselves.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For you were called to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29176X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29176X\"></sup>freedom, brethren; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29176Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29176Y\"></sup>only <i>do</i> not <i>turn</i> your freedom into an opportunity for the flesh, but through love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29176Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29176Z\"></sup>serve one another.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29177AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29177AA\"></sup>the whole Law is fulfilled in one word, in the <i>statement</i>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29177AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29177AB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall love your neighbor as yourself</span>.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29178AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29178AC\"></sup>bite and devour one another, take care that you are not consumed by one another.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But I say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29179AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29179AD\"></sup>walk by the Spirit, and you will not carry out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29179AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29179AE\"></sup>the desire of the flesh.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29180AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29180AF\"></sup>the flesh sets its desire against the Spirit, and the Spirit against the flesh; for these are in opposition to one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29180AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29180AG\"></sup>so that you may not do the things that you please.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But if you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29181AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29181AH\"></sup>led by the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29181AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29181AI\"></sup>you are not under the Law.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Now the deeds of the flesh are evident, which are: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29182AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29182AJ\"></sup>immorality, impurity, sensuality,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>idolatry, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29183AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29183AK\"></sup>sorcery, enmities, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29183AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29183AL\"></sup>strife, jealousy, outbursts of anger, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29183AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29183AM\"></sup>disputes, dissensions, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29183AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29183AN\"></sup>factions,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>envying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29184AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29184AO\"></sup>drunkenness, carousing, and things like these, of which I forewarn you, just as I have forewarned you, that those who practice such things will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29184AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29184AP\"></sup>inherit the kingdom of God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29185AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29185AQ\"></sup>the fruit of the Spirit is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29185AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29185AR\"></sup>love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness, faithfulness,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>gentleness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29186AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29186AS\"></sup>self-control; against such things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29186AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29186AT\"></sup>there is no law.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now those who belong to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29187AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29187AU\"></sup>Christ Jesus have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29187AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29187AV\"></sup>crucified the flesh with its passions and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29187AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29187AW\"></sup>desires.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>If we live by the Spirit, let us also walk <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29188AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29188AX\"></sup>by the Spirit.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Let us not become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29189AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29189AY\"></sup>boastful, challenging one another, envying one another."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29190A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29190A\"></sup>Brethren, even if anyone is caught in any trespass, you who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29190B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29190B\"></sup>spiritual, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29190C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29190C\"></sup>restore such a one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29190D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29190D\"></sup>in a spirit of gentleness; <i>each one</i> looking to yourself, so that you too will not be tempted.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29191E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29191E\"></sup>Bear one another’s burdens, and thereby fulfill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29191F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29191F\"></sup>the law of Christ.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29192G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29192G\"></sup>if anyone thinks he is something when he is nothing, he deceives himself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But each one must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29193H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29193H\"></sup>examine his own work, and then he will have <i>reason for</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29193I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29193I\"></sup>boasting in regard to himself alone, and not in regard to another.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29194J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29194J\"></sup>each one will bear his own load.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29195K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29195K\"></sup>The one who is taught <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29195L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29195L\"></sup>the word is to share all good things with the one who teaches <i>him</i>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29196M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29196M\"></sup>Do not be deceived, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29196N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29196N\"></sup>God is not mocked; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29196O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29196O\"></sup>whatever a man sows, this he will also reap.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29197P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29197P\"></sup>For the one who sows to his own flesh will from the flesh reap <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29197Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29197Q\"></sup>corruption, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29197R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29197R\"></sup>the one who sows to the Spirit will from the Spirit reap eternal life.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29198S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29198S\"></sup>Let us not lose heart in doing good, for in due time we will reap if we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29198T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29198T\"></sup>do not grow weary.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29199U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29199U\"></sup>while we have opportunity, let us do good to all people, and especially to those who are of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29199V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29199V\"></sup>household of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29199W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29199W\"></sup>the faith.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>See with what large letters I am writing to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29200X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29200X\"></sup>with my own hand.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Those who desire <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29201Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29201Y\"></sup>to make a good showing in the flesh try to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29201Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29201Z\"></sup>compel you to be circumcised, simply so that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29201AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29201AA\"></sup>will not be persecuted for the cross of Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For those who are circumcised do not even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29202AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29202AB\"></sup>keep the Law themselves, but they desire to have you circumcised so that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29202AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29202AC\"></sup>boast in your flesh.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29203AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29203AD\"></sup>may it never be that I would boast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29203AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29203AE\"></sup>except in the cross of our Lord Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29203AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29203AF\"></sup>through which the world has been crucified to me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29203AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29203AG\"></sup>I to the world.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29204AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29204AH\"></sup>neither is circumcision anything, nor uncircumcision, but a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29204AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29204AI\"></sup>new creation.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And those who will walk by this rule, peace and mercy <i>be</i> upon them, and upon the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29205AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29205AJ\"></sup>Israel of God.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>From now on let no one cause trouble for me, for I bear on my body the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29206AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29206AK\"></sup>brand-marks of Jesus.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29207AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29207AL\"></sup>The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29207AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29207AM\"></sup>with your spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29207AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29207AN\"></sup>brethren. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;